and <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">South Dakotans</ENAMEX> rebuffed an effort to stop financing <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">schools</ENAMEX> with property
taxes.

            <TIMEX TYPE="TIME">Five</TIMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">states</ENAMEX>--<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Arizona</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Maine</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Michigan</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">New Jersey</ENAMEX>, and <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">North Carolina</ENAMEX>--endorsed
