<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Arizona</ENAMEX>, animal baiting in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Missouri</ENAMEX>, and animal traps and horsemeat sales in
<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">California</ENAMEX>. (<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Alaska</ENAMEX> did reject a ban of wolf traps, and <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Ohioans</ENAMEX> voted to
