imposed a new waiting period for <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT_DESC">gun</ENAMEX> purchases. <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Arizona</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Massachusetts</ENAMEX> both
