<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Hampshire</ENAMEX> did not), and <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Florida</ENAMEX> passed an equal rights initiative. And, in the
"it may not sound like progress but it is" <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">department</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Utah</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">residents</ENAMEX>
