afflicted with a foolish optimism may view these initiative victories as a sign
of an impending liberal <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">majority</ENAMEX>. I suspect they represent something else: the
generosity of the prosperous. According to exit polls, <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">American</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">voters</ENAMEX> feel
